This song was originally composed and written by the Great Ustad Jalil Zaland, who is a famous Afghani singer and composer, he has written famous songs for both Iranian and Afghan singer in the 60's, 70's and until 90's. This particular song requested and was given as a gift to Googoosh during a royal music festival held during the Shah of Iran wife's annual festival during journey of the great Ustad. 

Source. Check out Ustad "Jalil Zaland" songs on YouTube.
